{"tid":1212207,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"戰術討論 韓國人教你如何在夢中抗爭","createTime":"2019-06-12T17:41:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-13T01:54:20.000Z","uid":62238,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"81ba8ac7882dd3c5d5138a88581fda347d5c8f92","tid":1212207,"uid":62238,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T17:41:35.000Z","msg":"發夢見到 今日好多人輸喺催淚彈度<br />\n冇錯，喺夢中係好多人好快整熄 仲有多人掉返過去<br />\n但係後排好多人頂唔順都散得好快 前線次次硬食 真係好孤立無援<br />\n不如大家都學下韓國學生點喺低成本少武器下抗爭<br />\n下次發返個好夢<br />\n<br />\n街頭抗爭的裝備，則非常原始簡陋，如果警方用<span style=\"color: red;\">水炮，便穿雨衣抵抗</span>。至於應付警方的<span style=\"color: green;\">催淚彈，就在鼻子下面抹一點牙膏，再戴上口罩</span>，<span style=\"color: orange;\">眼睛</span>防護則是罩上<span style=\"color: orange;\">透明膠袋</span>。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://indepth.mingpao.com/php/passage.php?seriesno=1&amp;titleno=1413310218463\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Findepth.mingpao.com%2Fphp%2Fpassage.php%3Fseriesno%3D1%26titleno%3D1413310218463&d=0lytrcPBTEnksf4YR0ybMZAoa2UDg2CF3RpsD8fDyZM%3D&h=17eae252\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Findepth.mingpao.com%2Fphp%2Fpassage.php%3Fseriesno%3D1%26titleno%3D1413310218463&h=336579e0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://indepth.mingpao.com/php/passage.php?seriesno=1&amp;titleno=1413310218463</a><br />\n<br />\n今次發唔到唔緊要，韓國人教你:<br />\n民主化沒有捷徑，學生要想辦法，用正當理由說服市民支持。<span style=\"color: pink;\">若能堅持下去，即使現在看起來不可能達成的目標，也有成功的一天</span><br />\n<br />\n歡迎大家一齊討論如何發個好夢"},{"pid":"68476093c5beb92c507df691e926bfc36f226ba9","tid":1212207,"uid":258377,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T17:49:52.000Z","msg":"雖然好撚憎泡菜狗加耶撚<br />\n但係物理攻擊＞韓國<br />\n魔法攻擊＞耶撚"},{"pid":"251a3ee0fc9a1a1db49c47ec371ccbd2b7611277","tid":1212207,"uid":24961,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T01:52:36.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"fed7b908907ab56cf3ec396cfe52cebdf7e56b4f","tid":1212207,"uid":163663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T01:5